;OS
OS {ok}


# Firefox OS;An open operating system for mobile devices.
Jun samajel q'inoj okel kichin ri taq asamajib'al richin oyonib'äl.


# Open Badges;A new standard to recognize and verify learning.
Jun k'ak'a' rub'eyal richin nino' chuwäch chuqa' ninik'öx ri etamab'äl.


# Marketplace;A creation and distribution platform for apps.
Jun nuk'uche'el richin kitz'ukik chuqa' kitaluxik taq chokoy.


# Persona;A better way to sign in to websites.
Jun utziläj chi rub'anikil richin nitikirisäx samaj pa taq ruxaq k'amaya'l.


# Thunderbird;Safe, fast and easy email.
Ri ütz, aninäq chuqa' man k'ayew ta rokisaxik chi taqoya'l.


# Webmaker;Make something amazing with the Web.
Tatz'uku' jun janila jeb'ël rik'in ri K'amaya'l.


# WebFWD;Our community-driven innovation accelerator.
Ri qapararenel richin tz'ukuj b'anon ruma ri molaj winaqi'.


# Labs;New ways to explore, experiment and innovate.
K'ak'a' taq rub'anikil richin rukanoxik, runa'onik chuqa' rujalnuk'ik.


# Bugzilla;A bug tracking system to help manage software development.
Jun q'inoj richin kikanoxik taq sachoj, ri nito'on chi ninuk' rub'anikil ri kema'.


# Firebug;Inspect, debug, analyze and more inside your browser.
Nutz'ët, nuchojmirisaj, nunik'oj chuqa' juley chik chupam ri awokik'amaya'l. 


# Gecko;The layout engine that drives Firefox.
Ri rusamajinel nuk'wachinïk ri nuq'alajisaj Firefox.


# XULRunner;An environment for XUL-based applications.
Jun kik'ojlemal ri taq chokoy, ri k'o kixe'el pa XUL.


